{"tid":1287512,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"淡友俠點樣上番車？！CCL > 190","createTime":"2019-07-05T08:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T15:07:58.000Z","uid":43146,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff23960f52ded7392ca683eba7486984fcace6f","tid":1287512,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:42:29.000Z","msg":"二手樓價再升，中原城市領先指數CCL最新報190.48點，按周升1.41%，連升3周再創歷史新高。以正式買賣合約日期計，2019年上半年CCL累升9.16%。 <br />\n<br />\n中原城市大型屋苑領先指數CCL Mass報191.58點，按周升1.53%。CCL(中小型單位)報190.19點，按周升1.47%。CCL(大型單位)報191.93點，按周升1.10%。CCL、CCL Mass及CCL(中小型單位)齊升3周，分別上升2.27%、2.28%及2.30%。 <br />\n<br />\n本周四區指數二升二跌。新界西CCL_Mass報174.59點，按周升1.86%，連升4周共2.30%。在剛需支持下，新界西樓價持續高企。港島CCL_Mass報199.24點，按周升5.69%，連升2周共6.62%。九龍CCL_Mass報185.72點，按周跌0.95%，連升2周後回軟。新界東CCL_Mass報199.35點，按周跌0.30%，連跌2周共0.82%。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y27h2WX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy27h2WX.png&h=7d6f9698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tha7FJK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTha7FJK.png&h=5c3daf4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3a6b6fb438e6040e18b43d40614f1402c93803e","tid":1287512,"uid":50502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"認真一問 大陸長期放大陸人落黎 樓價貴一貴都掃 香港人又要住局買<br />\n咁落去係咪樓價係咪無限咁升上去 直到大陸富商都覺貴先停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209fe67161ca15c30fbd6df002049ae64f03d947","tid":1287512,"uid":110904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:46:41.000Z","msg":"Yeah <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae31aee8fb652e679ce728f09e14896ce30edac","tid":1287512,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:08:49.000Z","msg":"佢宣佈左淡友勝出"},{"pid":"0b5ce1625ad6a20866329ab8d7701f03862293c4","tid":1287512,"uid":43146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3a6b6fb438e6040e18b